                            <div style="font-size:16px;">
                                <p>Dear <span t-field="o.name"/></p>
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                <p>As you are aware, your employment was subject to a probationary period.</p>
                                <br/>
                                <p>During this period your performance has been assessed against the Companyâ€™s standard of conduct, attendance and job performance. I am pleased to confirm that you have successfully completed your probation.</p>
                                <br/>
                                <p>This letter is a confirmation of your appointment to the position of 
                                <t t-if=" not o.employee_position_id">
                                    <span>_______________________</span>
                                </t>
                                <t t-if="o.employee_position_id">
                                    <span t-field="o.employee_position_id.name"/>
                                </t>
                                as of date <span t-field="o.probation_end_date"/></p> 
                                <br/>
                                <br/>
                                <p>Thank you for your contribution to SISB.</p>
                                <br/><br/>
                                <br/>
                                <p>Yours sincerely,</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </t>
            </t>
        </template>

